s in the past, we arrive at the\nslope and value of the symmetry energy at normal density of $70<L<101\\,\n\\text{MeV}$ and $33.5<a_a^V<36.4\\, \\text{MeV}$, respectively.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2016 01:58:01 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Wed, 23 Nov 2016 20:28:27 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-13"}
