n with the 181-second period. Due to high\nbeam velocity (~c/3, where c is the light speed) the 25-500 MHz radio emission,\ncorresponding to a large interval of heights in the solar corona, is nearly\nsynchronous.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Mon, 7 Nov 2016 14:41:01 GMT"}],"update_date":"2016-12-14"}
